            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Hard bounces are caused by invalid or mistyped email addresses (e.g. user@gmaill.com), deleted or deactivated accounts, non-existent domains, or permanent blocks by the receiving mail server.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
